1
00:00:02,669 --> 00:00:04,463
[theme music plays]

2
00:01:25,377 --> 00:01:28,297
I feel you're the first friend
that I have ever had.

3
00:01:28,589 --> 00:01:29,673
[both exclaiming]

4
00:01:32,843 --> 00:01:34,261
-Misa.
-Yes?

5
00:01:34,511 --> 00:01:35,804
Then, could you ask Rem

6
00:01:36,388 --> 00:01:37,764
to kill L?

7
00:01:37,973 --> 00:01:38,974
Huh?

8
00:01:39,141 --> 00:01:40,183
Rem…

9
00:01:40,601 --> 00:01:42,144
I want Light to love me.

10
00:01:42,269 --> 00:01:44,396
And I know we could be happy together.

11
00:01:45,188 --> 00:01:46,315
It's all I ever wanted.

12
00:01:47,232 --> 00:01:48,525
That's fine.

13
00:01:48,859 --> 00:01:50,819
I'll kill L for you.

14
00:01:51,445 --> 00:01:52,904
[Light] L will die...

15
00:01:53,739 --> 00:01:55,991
That's all it took.

16
00:01:56,074 --> 00:01:58,994
WAGER

17
00:02:00,078 --> 00:02:02,039
-[Rem] So, when should I kill him?
-[gasps]

18
00:02:02,414 --> 00:02:06,376
If you take me to where he is,
I can kill him immediately.

19
00:02:06,543 --> 00:02:08,128
The sooner, the better.

20
00:02:08,462 --> 00:02:09,379
Maybe tomorrow.

21
00:02:09,546 --> 00:02:13,175
Hmm. I should think this through
before we do anything.

22
00:02:14,468 --> 00:02:16,887
I need tonight to decide
how we're going to kill L.

23
00:02:17,012 --> 00:02:18,430
I'll give you my answer tomorrow.

24
00:02:18,722 --> 00:02:19,723
[Rem] Very well.

25
00:02:20,098 --> 00:02:21,808
[Light] Also, no matter what,

26
00:02:21,933 --> 00:02:24,436
you can't kill him until I give the order.

27
00:02:24,895 --> 00:02:26,438
No matter what. Understood?

28
00:02:26,980 --> 00:02:29,399
[Rem] All right. I'll promise you that.

29
00:02:29,983 --> 00:02:31,693
At least where L is concerned.

30
00:02:32,486 --> 00:02:35,197
Misa, I need you to give me
your cellphone number.

31
00:02:35,489 --> 00:02:37,616
About time! What took you so long?

32
00:02:37,699 --> 00:02:39,076
Give me yours too, okay?

33
00:02:39,284 --> 00:02:41,578
No, Misa, I'm afraid I can't do that.

34
00:02:41,912 --> 00:02:42,913
Why not?

35
00:02:43,038 --> 00:02:45,040
I'm your girlfriend!
I should have your number.

36
00:02:45,248 --> 00:02:48,543
I already told you,
I'm under surveillance by the police.

37
00:02:48,794 --> 00:02:52,881
Keep in mind, it's not difficult for them
to bug even cellphones these days.

38
00:02:53,256 --> 00:02:54,341
Oh...

39
00:02:54,758 --> 00:02:58,011
Okay then, what about this?
I'll just give you one of my phones.

40
00:02:58,095 --> 00:02:59,554
I ended up with three of them.

41
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:01,556
'Cause I use them for different things.

42
00:03:02,849 --> 00:03:04,101
Yeah, good idea.

43
00:03:04,267 --> 00:03:06,478
If we use yours, I think we'll be safe.

44
00:03:06,728 --> 00:03:10,524
That's great! I can hear your voice
every day, and text you too!

45
00:03:10,774 --> 00:03:12,609
No, I'll keep this one turned off.

46
00:03:12,693 --> 00:03:16,905
I'll be the only one making the calls,
and only when it's absolutely necessary.

47
00:03:17,364 --> 00:03:18,824
What? No way.

48
00:03:19,908 --> 00:03:21,702
Then when are you gonna call me?

49
00:03:22,077 --> 00:03:23,912
-Probably tomorrow.
-Huh?

50
00:03:24,037 --> 00:03:26,540
That will most likely be the day
we execute L,

51
00:03:26,665 --> 00:03:28,125
but I'll call you either way.

52
00:03:28,417 --> 00:03:29,793
What? Tomorrow?

53
00:03:30,085 --> 00:03:31,753
It doesn't sound like a very romantic call

54
00:03:31,837 --> 00:03:34,047
but I suppose we can always
talk about us afterwards.

55
00:03:34,381 --> 00:03:36,967
Well, I think you should probably
go home now, Misa.

56
00:03:37,217 --> 00:03:39,594
Huh? But why? It's only seven o'clock.

57
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:42,139
The time for lovers
is just beginning, you know?

58
00:03:42,222 --> 00:03:45,350
We can go for a romantic dinner,
then maybe a moonlight stroll in the park,

59
00:03:45,434 --> 00:03:47,144
and after that, the main event!

60
00:03:47,602 --> 00:03:48,687
-Misa.
-Huh?

61
00:03:48,937 --> 00:03:49,938
[gasps]

62
00:03:50,188 --> 00:03:52,023
[Ryuk chuckling] Wow.

63
00:03:59,364 --> 00:04:00,449
Listen.

64
00:04:00,949 --> 00:04:02,534
You have to go home now.

65
00:04:03,368 --> 00:04:04,286
Okay.

66
00:04:04,745 --> 00:04:07,330
Also, when you're talking to Rem outside,

67
00:04:07,664 --> 00:04:09,875
be careful that no one's around to listen.

68
00:04:09,958 --> 00:04:11,042
Just whisper.

69
00:04:11,376 --> 00:04:13,128
That's what I always do with Ryuk.

70
00:04:13,420 --> 00:04:14,421
Okay.

71
00:04:14,838 --> 00:04:16,715
Bye bye! Have a good night.

72
00:04:16,840 --> 00:04:19,926
Bye bye, Misa! Come again real soon!

73
00:04:23,430 --> 00:04:26,141
[Ryuk chuckles]
That kiss came out of nowhere.

74
00:04:26,391 --> 00:04:29,936
[Light] Sure. It's very important
that Misa stays infatuated with me.

75
00:04:30,061 --> 00:04:31,229
[Ryuk] Oh?

76
00:04:31,354 --> 00:04:34,274
More importantly, I need to decide
if L should die tomorrow.

77
00:04:35,192 --> 00:04:37,944
Since he hasn't gone public yet,
if Ryuga dies,

78
00:04:38,069 --> 00:04:40,864
the other Task Force members
will be suspicious of me.

79
00:04:41,114 --> 00:04:42,991
So I have to make sure I'm prepared.

80
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,242
[Ryuk] I see.

81
00:04:44,659 --> 00:04:46,787
I thought perhaps you were hesitating

82
00:04:47,078 --> 00:04:49,414
because he said he thinks of you
as a friend.

83
00:04:49,873 --> 00:04:52,876
[chuckles] A friend?
I just gave him what he wanted.

84
00:04:53,084 --> 00:04:55,420
From the start, I've said
if it's my friendship he wants,

85
00:04:55,504 --> 00:04:57,714
I'd give it to him
as a way to win his trust.

86
00:04:58,548 --> 00:05:01,343
Ryuga and Light Yagami
appear to be friends.

87
00:05:01,676 --> 00:05:03,261
But L is Kira's enemy.

88
00:05:12,604 --> 00:05:15,315
[Light] That's right.
Ryuga revealed that he is L.

89
00:05:15,565 --> 00:05:17,442
Therefore, he must die.

90
00:05:19,402 --> 00:05:21,404
If I have him die in an accident,

91
00:05:21,738 --> 00:05:24,658
chances are that less people
will suspect I'm Kira.

92
00:05:24,908 --> 00:05:27,702
And even if they do, there'd be no proof.

93
00:05:28,036 --> 00:05:30,872
I can only speculate
what will happen after he dies.

94
00:05:31,456 --> 00:05:35,961
Tomorrow will be L's,
or at least Ryuga and Ryuzaki's...

95
00:05:36,169 --> 00:05:37,796
last day alive.

96
00:05:47,931 --> 00:05:49,307
Hair.

97
00:05:49,432 --> 00:05:50,600
Hmm...

98
00:05:51,685 --> 00:05:54,271
[L sniffs] Snack crumbs.

99
00:05:57,023 --> 00:05:58,149
[L] Hair.

100
00:05:59,693 --> 00:06:01,069
-Mr. Yagami.
-Huh?

101
00:06:02,279 --> 00:06:05,824
If I die within the next few days,
your son is Kira.

102
00:06:06,491 --> 00:06:08,076
Oh, another hair.

103
00:06:08,326 --> 00:06:09,578
[gasps]

104
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,955
What did you just say, Ryuzaki?

105
00:06:12,247 --> 00:06:14,457
Exactly.
What are you talking about anyway?

106
00:06:14,791 --> 00:06:18,003
If anything happens to me, I have asked
Watari to make himself available to you.

107
00:06:18,086 --> 00:06:19,921
So, I'm counting on you, team.

108
00:06:20,005 --> 00:06:20,881
Ryuzaki!

109
00:06:21,256 --> 00:06:23,633
You said he was almost cleared,
and now this?

110
00:06:23,884 --> 00:06:26,219
Honestly, how much do you suspect my son?

111
00:06:26,928 --> 00:06:29,848
Hmm, the truth is, I don't even know
what to think anymore.

112
00:06:29,931 --> 00:06:30,807
Huh?

113
00:06:31,099 --> 00:06:33,393
I've never been in a situation like this.

114
00:06:34,185 --> 00:06:37,063
If Kira and the Second Kira
are working together right now,

115
00:06:37,147 --> 00:06:38,690
things are not looking good for me.

116
00:06:39,065 --> 00:06:40,358
Given that,

117
00:06:40,901 --> 00:06:43,486
I may not be thinking
as clearly as I normally do,

118
00:06:43,570 --> 00:06:44,863
so I could be wrong.

119
00:06:45,530 --> 00:06:46,948
[slurps loudly]

120
00:06:47,991 --> 00:06:51,703
Maybe I still consider him a suspect
only because we don't have anyone else.

121
00:06:52,621 --> 00:06:53,872
But still...

122
00:06:54,581 --> 00:06:58,793
if I do happen to be killed soon,
please assume that your son is Kira.

123
00:06:58,919 --> 00:06:59,961
[all grunting]

124
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:05,258
[L] I have no choice
but to make a sneak attack.

125
00:07:06,343 --> 00:07:08,011
This is all a wager now.

126
00:07:15,685 --> 00:07:17,520
[birds twittering]

127
00:07:17,729 --> 00:07:19,439
[indistinct chatter]

128
00:07:19,689 --> 00:07:21,942
[Light chuckles] I wouldn't say that.

129
00:07:22,525 --> 00:07:24,778
I just know how to get by, that's all.

130
00:07:24,903 --> 00:07:26,112
[gasps]

131
00:07:28,990 --> 00:07:30,742
Hey, what's wrong?

132
00:07:35,455 --> 00:07:37,749
Ah! Hey, Light!

133
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,126
How's it going?

134
00:07:40,502 --> 00:07:41,962
[sighs]

135
00:07:42,379 --> 00:07:46,633
Kiyomi, could we continue this later?
I need a moment alone with him.

136
00:07:46,967 --> 00:07:48,343
Uh, okay.

137
00:07:52,263 --> 00:07:54,140
I hope she's not upset.

138
00:07:54,724 --> 00:07:56,726
Never mind that. Is it okay to be here?

139
00:07:56,893 --> 00:07:59,396
Didn't you say you were afraid
to appear in public?

140
00:07:59,980 --> 00:08:03,191
Yeah, I did. But then I realized
that as long as you're not Kira,

141
00:08:03,358 --> 00:08:04,359
I should be safe.

142
00:08:04,484 --> 00:08:07,612
The fact is, you're the only one
on the outside who knows me as L.

143
00:08:07,988 --> 00:08:11,282
In the unlikely event
that I die in the next few days,

144
00:08:11,491 --> 00:08:13,368
I've instructed your father
and everyone at headquarters,

145
00:08:13,702 --> 00:08:15,620
to assume that you are Kira.

146
00:08:17,372 --> 00:08:18,665
Damn him.

147
00:08:21,167 --> 00:08:22,711
Besides, you told me yourself

148
00:08:22,794 --> 00:08:24,754
that you missed having me around
at school.

149
00:08:24,921 --> 00:08:28,049
So I figured, why not come back
for a little change of pace?

150
00:08:28,258 --> 00:08:31,177
As long as it doesn't kill me,
college is a lot of fun.

151
00:08:31,469 --> 00:08:33,471
[Light] I have to admit,
without you around,

152
00:08:33,555 --> 00:08:35,974
intelligent conversation
is hard to come by.

153
00:08:36,349 --> 00:08:38,893
[L chuckles] I see. Luckily,
Kiyomi's there to fill the void.

154
00:08:39,019 --> 00:08:40,729
[Light] Well, something like that.

155
00:08:40,937 --> 00:08:42,439
[Ryuk laughs]

156
00:08:42,564 --> 00:08:45,734
[Light] Now I don't know.
Is it still okay to kill him today?

157
00:08:46,401 --> 00:08:50,030
No. As soon as I make the decision
to kill him, he suddenly appears.

158
00:08:50,113 --> 00:08:52,615
Almost as if to distract me from my goal.

159
00:08:53,074 --> 00:08:55,201
I guess he's trying to guarantee
his safety.

160
00:08:55,744 --> 00:08:58,913
And the way things are,
I'm playing right into his hands.

161
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:02,667
Hey, do you want to have some cake
with me in the cafeteria?

162
00:09:03,001 --> 00:09:05,128
Sure. I have a break now anyway.

163
00:09:05,587 --> 00:09:08,256
Um, that's perfect.
I'm kinda craving shortcake right now.

164
00:09:10,842 --> 00:09:12,844
Well, let's hope they have it.

165
00:09:13,428 --> 00:09:15,513
[Misa] Light! There you are!

166
00:09:15,805 --> 00:09:19,184
I had a photo-shoot nearby,
so I thought I'd come by to see you.

167
00:09:19,434 --> 00:09:21,394
[Light] Misa, you idiot!

168
00:09:21,561 --> 00:09:23,688
Oh, this must be a friend of yours.

169
00:09:23,772 --> 00:09:25,815
He looks so different. Unique.

170
00:09:26,107 --> 00:09:28,026
Wait! I've won!

171
00:09:28,610 --> 00:09:31,404
Misa will be able to see
Ryuga's real name!

172
00:09:31,946 --> 00:09:34,616
Hi there. I'm Light's girlfriend,
Misa Amane.

173
00:09:34,699 --> 00:09:35,784
Nice to meet you.

174
00:09:36,159 --> 00:09:37,452
I'm Hideki Ryuga.

175
00:09:38,078 --> 00:09:40,205
Huh? Hideki Ryuga?

176
00:09:40,371 --> 00:09:42,373
Yeah, he has the exact same
first and last name

177
00:09:42,540 --> 00:09:44,042
as the famous idol.

178
00:09:44,167 --> 00:09:45,376
Pretty bizarre, huh?

179
00:09:46,002 --> 00:09:48,463
[Misa] But it's different
than the name I'm seeing.

180
00:09:49,714 --> 00:09:50,799
[Light] Ryuga,

181
00:09:50,965 --> 00:09:54,886
deciding to come here today
was a mistake. Huh?

182
00:09:55,095 --> 00:09:57,889
[laughing softly]

183
00:09:58,389 --> 00:09:59,891
Why the hell is he laughing?

184
00:10:00,433 --> 00:10:02,477
Could it mean he noticed something?

185
00:10:02,977 --> 00:10:04,270
But it makes no sense.

186
00:10:04,437 --> 00:10:06,523
If he somehow guessed
that she's the Second Kira,

187
00:10:06,606 --> 00:10:08,650
there's no way he'd be laughing right now.

188
00:10:08,983 --> 00:10:11,444
[chuckles] Light...

189
00:10:12,946 --> 00:10:13,988
You're a lucky guy.

190
00:10:14,489 --> 00:10:15,490
[Light gasps]

191
00:10:15,782 --> 00:10:18,952
I have been a huge fan of yours
ever since the August issue of Eighteen.

192
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:21,204
What? Really? That's so sweet of you.

193
00:10:21,412 --> 00:10:23,790
Hey! Oh my God,
isn't that girl Misa-Misa?

194
00:10:23,957 --> 00:10:25,542
You're right! It's her!

195
00:10:25,834 --> 00:10:27,293
[girl] She's so cute!

196
00:10:27,377 --> 00:10:30,171
Wow, I should've guessed I'd be spotted
with all these kids around.

197
00:10:30,588 --> 00:10:32,048
I'm, like, your biggest fan!

198
00:10:32,173 --> 00:10:33,424
Keep up the good work.

199
00:10:33,508 --> 00:10:35,677
Thank you! Couldn't do it without you.

200
00:10:36,386 --> 00:10:37,512
What is this?

201
00:10:37,804 --> 00:10:40,140
No way! Somebody just touched my butt!

202
00:10:40,598 --> 00:10:42,100
Uh...

203
00:10:42,517 --> 00:10:43,726
This is an outrage!

204
00:10:43,852 --> 00:10:46,396
Taking advantage of this situation
is unforgivable.

205
00:10:46,563 --> 00:10:49,065
I will find whoever
is responsible for this.

206
00:10:49,149 --> 00:10:50,400
[Misa giggles]

207
00:10:50,525 --> 00:10:52,443
Oh, Ryuga, you're so funny!

208
00:10:52,986 --> 00:10:54,821
-I want to touch her too.
-Stupid!

209
00:10:55,071 --> 00:10:58,616
I want to ask Misa what L's real name
is as soon as possible,

210
00:10:58,825 --> 00:11:00,785
but all these people are in the way.

211
00:11:01,661 --> 00:11:03,121
Misa!

212
00:11:03,371 --> 00:11:05,915
It's time! Or were you planning
to be late again?

213
00:11:06,207 --> 00:11:07,667
No. I'm sorry, Yoshi.

214
00:11:08,001 --> 00:11:10,086
-Let's go!
-Oh, okay.

215
00:11:10,879 --> 00:11:11,921
Perfect.

216
00:11:12,005 --> 00:11:13,798
Now that Misa's away from the crowd,

217
00:11:13,882 --> 00:11:16,676
I just have to give her a call
and ask for L's real name.

218
00:11:17,218 --> 00:11:19,512
Bye, Light! I'll see you after work.

219
00:11:19,596 --> 00:11:21,139
Miss you already. [giggles]

220
00:11:26,519 --> 00:11:28,688
Now then, perhaps we should get going.

221
00:11:28,980 --> 00:11:29,939
Yeah.

222
00:11:30,356 --> 00:11:31,900
Actually, could you go on ahead?

223
00:11:32,025 --> 00:11:33,651
I need to go use the restroom.

224
00:11:34,068 --> 00:11:35,945
Oh, okay then. I'll see you there.

225
00:11:49,918 --> 00:11:51,169
It's over.

226
00:11:52,170 --> 00:11:55,048
It's been fun… L.

227
00:11:55,757 --> 00:11:58,509
I'm grateful that I was the one
to discover your name

228
00:11:59,093 --> 00:12:01,262
so I could kill you myself.

229
00:12:22,825 --> 00:12:25,036
[Light] L, it's been fun.

230
00:12:25,787 --> 00:12:28,790
I'm grateful that I was the one
to discover your name

231
00:12:28,873 --> 00:12:31,084
so I could kill you myself.

232
00:12:31,292 --> 00:12:32,418
[phone beeps]

233
00:12:35,630 --> 00:12:40,426
[phone ringing]

234
00:12:41,427 --> 00:12:47,934
[pop music ringtone playing]

235
00:12:54,816 --> 00:12:57,735
[ ringtone continues playing]

236
00:12:58,861 --> 00:13:00,905
Yes, hello?

237
00:13:02,115 --> 00:13:03,658
What do you mean, "Hello"?

238
00:13:04,033 --> 00:13:05,368
Oh, is that you, Light?

239
00:13:05,451 --> 00:13:07,287
I guess someone must have
dropped this phone

240
00:13:07,370 --> 00:13:08,997
in all of the commotion earlier on.

241
00:13:09,330 --> 00:13:11,791
He took it. Bastard!

242
00:13:16,337 --> 00:13:17,463
Uh, hello?

243
00:13:17,714 --> 00:13:20,842
[Light] Yeah.
That's Misa's cellphone you have.

244
00:13:21,134 --> 00:13:24,429
-I can give it back to her.
-I see. Sure, that makes sense.

245
00:13:25,388 --> 00:13:26,764
[hangs up]

246
00:13:30,059 --> 00:13:30,935
Ryuga...

247
00:13:31,019 --> 00:13:33,479
He probably thinks he's pretty clever
right now.

248
00:13:33,604 --> 00:13:36,357
But Misa has another phone
he doesn't know about.

249
00:13:36,524 --> 00:13:38,151
I'll just call that one instead.

250
00:13:38,234 --> 00:13:39,152
[phone ringing]

251
00:13:39,235 --> 00:13:42,280
[L] Oh, this time
it's actually my cellphone.

252
00:13:42,947 --> 00:13:44,699
[clears throat] Yes?

253
00:13:45,867 --> 00:13:46,993
Yes, I see.

254
00:13:47,410 --> 00:13:48,786
So, it's done then?

255
00:13:49,912 --> 00:13:50,997
I understand.

256
00:13:54,042 --> 00:13:55,835
I'm not exactly sure how you'll take this,

257
00:13:55,918 --> 00:13:58,463
but regarding Misa Amane,
there's something you should know.

258
00:13:59,047 --> 00:14:02,467
We've taken her into custody
under suspicion of being the Second Kira.

259
00:14:03,593 --> 00:14:04,719
[Ryuk chuckles]

260
00:14:05,219 --> 00:14:07,513
[Light] How long has he known about Misa?

261
00:14:07,680 --> 00:14:09,891
I never thought
he'd find her this quickly.

262
00:14:11,059 --> 00:14:12,477
We gathered physical evidence

263
00:14:12,560 --> 00:14:15,188
from the envelopes that were sent
by the Second Kira.

264
00:14:15,646 --> 00:14:17,982
In particular,
we recovered hairs and fibers

265
00:14:18,107 --> 00:14:19,984
from the masking tape used to seal them.

266
00:14:20,151 --> 00:14:22,028
They matched what we found in Misa's room.

267
00:14:22,653 --> 00:14:24,113
There would be a public uproar

268
00:14:24,197 --> 00:14:26,866
if it gets out that she's been apprehended
as the Second Kira.

269
00:14:27,075 --> 00:14:30,078
So, officially, we've charged her manager
with drug possession

270
00:14:30,161 --> 00:14:31,704
and she's a voluntary witness.

271
00:14:32,246 --> 00:14:34,082
But I doubt any of this would get out.

272
00:14:37,085 --> 00:14:38,294
[Light] I was careless.

273
00:14:38,628 --> 00:14:39,670
The videos...

274
00:14:39,754 --> 00:14:41,464
I should have destroyed all the evidence

275
00:14:41,547 --> 00:14:43,508
before the police had a chance
to go through it.

276
00:14:44,884 --> 00:14:47,512
In the end,
Ryuga knew that his best defense

277
00:14:47,595 --> 00:14:50,098
was to stay close to me
rather than trying to hide.

278
00:14:50,306 --> 00:14:51,933
He confronted things head on.

279
00:14:53,226 --> 00:14:55,478
This wager was my...

280
00:14:55,853 --> 00:14:57,063
[L] Was my…

281
00:14:57,563 --> 00:14:58,648
Was my…

282
00:14:59,857 --> 00:15:01,442
-No!
-[gasps]

283
00:15:02,860 --> 00:15:03,945
Not yet.

284
00:15:04,570 --> 00:15:07,532
The real battle is just beginning, L.

285
00:15:16,582 --> 00:15:19,502
[sighs] Watari, has she said anything yet?

286
00:15:19,669 --> 00:15:21,629
[Watari] No, she hasn't spoken a word.

287
00:15:22,255 --> 00:15:23,923
Get me a visual of her, will you?

288
00:15:24,215 --> 00:15:25,299
Are you sure?

289
00:15:25,383 --> 00:15:26,592
Yes, and quickly.

290
00:15:28,219 --> 00:15:29,095
[exclaiming]

291
00:15:29,303 --> 00:15:34,684
[whimpering]

292
00:15:35,017 --> 00:15:37,228
[Mogi] Ryuzaki!
What's the meaning of this?

293
00:15:38,646 --> 00:15:41,732
[L] I've apprehended her on suspicion
of being the Second Kira.

294
00:15:41,858 --> 00:15:43,443
I'm afraid this is necessary.

295
00:15:43,901 --> 00:15:45,820
Chances are Amane is guilty.

296
00:15:46,195 --> 00:15:49,407
There seems to be enough evidence
to convict her, but all the same...

297
00:15:50,241 --> 00:15:52,076
Yes, there can be no mistake.

298
00:15:52,410 --> 00:15:54,537
Now we need a confession out of her.

299
00:15:54,871 --> 00:15:57,665
We need to know how she kills,
whether she knows Kira...

300
00:15:57,915 --> 00:15:59,667
and, if so, who he really is.

301
00:16:00,168 --> 00:16:02,587
Watari, take the necessary precautions,

302
00:16:02,670 --> 00:16:05,131
but beyond that, you're free to do
whatever has to be done, okay?

303
00:16:05,798 --> 00:16:07,008
Just make her speak.

304
00:16:07,133 --> 00:16:08,050
[Watari] Very well.

305
00:16:08,134 --> 00:16:09,886
-[L] Oh, and Mr. Yagami?
-Huh?

306
00:16:10,344 --> 00:16:12,388
Light has now become our prime suspect

307
00:16:12,513 --> 00:16:15,183
and I'm probably gonna bring him in
for interrogation as well.

308
00:16:15,725 --> 00:16:17,143
Please, be prepared for that.

309
00:16:17,268 --> 00:16:18,269
[grunts]

310
00:16:37,622 --> 00:16:39,957
[Watari] Ryuzaki, Amane is talking.

311
00:16:40,208 --> 00:16:42,793
Huh? Quickly, get me a visual and audio!

312
00:16:43,044 --> 00:16:45,213
[panting and grunting]

313
00:16:45,421 --> 00:16:47,381
[Aizawa] Finally,
after three days of this, huh?

314
00:16:48,966 --> 00:16:50,927
[Misa whimpering]

315
00:16:51,093 --> 00:16:52,720
[Misa] I can't take it anymore.

316
00:16:54,305 --> 00:16:55,181
Kill me.

317
00:16:55,348 --> 00:16:56,557
[all gasping]

318
00:16:56,849 --> 00:16:59,268
Kill me. Please, just kill me!

319
00:17:00,311 --> 00:17:03,564
I don't know, maybe this was all too much
for a young girl to take.

320
00:17:04,232 --> 00:17:06,025
He's right. We've pushed her too far.

321
00:17:07,485 --> 00:17:09,779
[L, distorted voice]
Misa Amane, can you hear me?

322
00:17:10,363 --> 00:17:11,531
[Misa] I hear you.

323
00:17:11,906 --> 00:17:13,950
Please, just kill me now.

324
00:17:15,076 --> 00:17:17,245
Does this mean you admit
to being the Second Kira?

325
00:17:17,328 --> 00:17:19,038
Is this the reason you wish to die?

326
00:17:19,330 --> 00:17:22,875
[Misa] No! I don't know anything
about the Second Kira.

327
00:17:23,584 --> 00:17:25,503
I really can't take this anymore!

328
00:17:25,753 --> 00:17:27,255
I'd rather be dead.

329
00:17:28,548 --> 00:17:30,091
Now, hurry up and kill me!

330
00:17:30,800 --> 00:17:33,469
If you wanted to, you could kill me
right now, couldn't you?

331
00:17:36,013 --> 00:17:38,015
Misa, do you mean...?

332
00:17:38,391 --> 00:17:40,017
Yes, kill me.

333
00:17:40,726 --> 00:17:42,770
Do you really mean that, Misa?

334
00:17:43,437 --> 00:17:45,022
Yes, I do.

335
00:17:47,358 --> 00:17:50,111
I can't take it anymore. Kill me.

336
00:17:51,195 --> 00:17:54,031
If I do this, then Light Yagami dies too.

337
00:17:54,532 --> 00:17:55,992
This is all his fault.

338
00:17:56,284 --> 00:17:58,119
You can't. No, you can't.

339
00:17:58,452 --> 00:17:59,620
Please, just kill me.

340
00:18:00,079 --> 00:18:01,163
Why, Misa?

341
00:18:01,414 --> 00:18:03,249
Why do you want to die for him?

342
00:18:05,459 --> 00:18:06,586
[Misa] Fine!

343
00:18:06,877 --> 00:18:08,087
If you won't kill me…

344
00:18:08,296 --> 00:18:10,298
Stop her!
Watari, don't let her bite her tongue!

345
00:18:10,840 --> 00:18:12,341
[exclaiming]

346
00:18:12,633 --> 00:18:15,136
[muffled yelling]

347
00:18:15,344 --> 00:18:17,054
[all grunting]

348
00:18:17,847 --> 00:18:19,265
Is it possible that this behavior

349
00:18:19,390 --> 00:18:22,518
could be attributed to Kira
controlling her actions before death?

350
00:18:23,894 --> 00:18:25,021
[Ryuk] Oh.

351
00:18:25,313 --> 00:18:26,689
What's the matter, Rem?

352
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:30,735
Light Yagami…

353
00:18:31,694 --> 00:18:34,780
Misa has refused my offer
to help her escape.

354
00:18:35,197 --> 00:18:37,950
No doubt because she knows
it would cause you trouble,

355
00:18:38,326 --> 00:18:40,828
since the police would then have
proof of her powers.

356
00:18:42,455 --> 00:18:45,333
When her suffering became more
than she could bear,

357
00:18:45,416 --> 00:18:47,501
she started begging me to kill her.

358
00:18:50,463 --> 00:18:53,049
All of this because she wants you
to love her.

359
00:18:56,010 --> 00:18:58,971
I could not possibly
let it go on like that.

360
00:18:59,388 --> 00:19:01,140
I couldn't bring myself to do it.

361
00:19:02,058 --> 00:19:05,144
There was only one way
to save her from her suffering.

362
00:19:06,020 --> 00:19:08,397
Forfeiting ownership of the Death Note.

363
00:19:09,106 --> 00:19:10,024
Yes.

364
00:19:10,524 --> 00:19:13,194
If Misa forfeits ownership
of the Death Note,

365
00:19:13,736 --> 00:19:16,781
all her memories related to it
would disappear.

366
00:19:17,156 --> 00:19:19,492
All the murders she committed with it.

367
00:19:19,867 --> 00:19:21,369
The fact that you are Kira.

368
00:19:21,494 --> 00:19:23,621
All those memories would be gone.

369
00:19:24,080 --> 00:19:26,165
Your secret would be safe.

370
00:19:28,125 --> 00:19:32,630
Also, Misa would no longer
be able to see Ryuk or me either.

371
00:19:34,131 --> 00:19:35,216
SEVERAL HOURS EARLIER

372
00:19:35,341 --> 00:19:36,384
Misa…

373
00:19:36,926 --> 00:19:40,137
When this is done, you'll forget
everything about Shinigami

374
00:19:40,221 --> 00:19:41,389
and the Death Note.

375
00:19:41,681 --> 00:19:43,849
[Misa, muffled speech]

376
00:19:44,016 --> 00:19:45,226
It's okay.

377
00:19:45,768 --> 00:19:48,771
The human being who you love
is Light Yagami.

378
00:19:49,438 --> 00:19:51,732
I promise those feelings will remain.

379
00:19:52,358 --> 00:19:53,567
[muffled sigh]

380
00:19:54,860 --> 00:19:56,070
So, Misa...

381
00:19:56,487 --> 00:19:58,823
forfeit ownership of the Death Note

382
00:19:59,073 --> 00:20:01,450
and leave everything to Light Yagami.

383
00:20:03,411 --> 00:20:04,578
[muffled] Okay.

384
00:20:22,430 --> 00:20:23,764
Huh?

385
00:20:24,849 --> 00:20:26,058
Hmm...

386
00:20:34,024 --> 00:20:37,570
And so, Misa is no longer
the owner of the Death Note.

387
00:20:38,195 --> 00:20:39,739
You did the right thing, Rem.

388
00:20:40,072 --> 00:20:43,367
I was beginning to think that was
the only way out of this situation.

389
00:20:44,034 --> 00:20:46,036
If her memories of the Death Note
are gone,

390
00:20:46,162 --> 00:20:48,831
then chances are they'll have
to release her eventually.

391
00:20:49,749 --> 00:20:51,000
Light Yagami,

392
00:20:51,208 --> 00:20:54,795
I proposed this to Misa
knowing it was exactly what you wanted

393
00:20:54,879 --> 00:20:56,714
and that it would serve your purposes.

394
00:20:56,839 --> 00:20:58,758
But I did so on one condition.

395
00:21:00,134 --> 00:21:02,428
And that is, if you don't save Misa,

396
00:21:02,511 --> 00:21:03,804
I will kill you.

397
00:21:03,971 --> 00:21:04,930
[Ryuk chuckles]

398
00:21:12,605 --> 00:21:13,814
I understand.

399
00:21:14,440 --> 00:21:17,276
And I have a pretty good idea
of what L will do next.

400
00:21:18,152 --> 00:21:19,487
I have a plan.

401
00:21:22,615 --> 00:21:24,116
This is goodbye, Ryuk.

402
00:21:25,201 --> 00:21:26,327
Huh?

403
00:21:26,410 --> 00:21:31,457
TO BE CONTINUED

404
00:21:35,461 --> 00:21:38,756
[theme music plays]
